duties_responsibilities.duty: Assess and develop individual care plans for members in home or face-to-face settings.
Provide telephonic support at appropriate intervals based on member needs.
Serve as a patient advocate, addressing concerns and barriers.
Facilitate and promote high-quality, cost-effective outcomes for members.
Maintain accurate records and ensure legal compliance.
Assist as a mentor for new hires and demonstrate HIPAA understanding.
Work in a fast-paced environment with changing priorities.

education_certification.credential: RN with a FL valid licensure required
